{"tid":2068580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油塘油翠苑女子高處墮下亡/女子顯徑邨墮樓倒斃花槽/男子疑跳城門河消防蛙人搜救","createTime":"2020-06-17T19:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T21:57:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9c371455ee8c94698496e3c79e67f8fb46aab2","tid":2068580,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:53:25.000Z","msg":"昨日(17日)晚上10時許，姓嚴(32歲)女子在顯徑邨顯佑樓高處墮下；保安員及街坊聽聞巨響，發現女子倒臥在大廈入口旁的花槽上，奄奄一息，報警求助。救護員證實女事主不治，警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信她從上址走廊墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n今日(18日)凌晨1時許，一名女子報案稱，早前與一名男性友人在電話傾談，期間感到對方情緒極度失落，擔心他會自尋短見，投河自盡。警方及消防蛙人趕至沙田鄉事會路近沙燕橋對出的城門河搜索，暫時未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n今日(18日)2時35分，一名女子在油塘油翠苑漾美閣墮樓，飛墮平台上。救護員接報到場，經檢查後證實事主已經死亡。警員封鎖現場，並登樓調查事主身份及墮樓原因。"},{"pid":"896413e1cf9d5848c9b37da0ca4b8c63ded68b7a","tid":2068580,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278e80aea5a1d60483d7fd087c43696816326c30","tid":2068580,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:42:59.000Z","msg":"希望個男人無事"},{"pid":"aba823fde4904cb4b5ea18790ef6faf110a3f772","tid":2068580,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:37:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73895da68c7fed07aa230efc5f0bfeaf58d7c7c2","tid":2068580,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3e2b51c74e607d8c772c60ef8b59a930884a55","tid":2068580,"uid":360826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\